<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">为大力弘扬工匠精神，表彰先进，树立优秀榜样，展示我校学生的技能水平，营造崇尚技能的学习氛围。11月9日，我校在学术报告厅隆重举行第九届职业技能大比武表彰会。执行校长范红铭、副校长高建国、梅龙以及各学院（部）负责人出席会议。会议由副校长徐国荣主持。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-10%2020%3A04%3A143111d2e1e84154b7e1a1462f7a523c8.jpg?Expires=2014977854&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=iaOsP8uU5CXyX1N8si9VwiNH%2B30%3D" alt="" width="650" height="366" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">会上，副校长高建国宣读了《关于表彰我校第九届职业技能大比武的获奖师生的决定》。本届技能大比武共305名学生获奖，其中刘晗怡等50名同学获一等奖，应灵等103名同学获二等奖，肖文清等152名同学获三等奖。李书烨等28名老师获优秀指导老师奖。副校长徐国荣、高建国、梅龙为技能大比武获奖学生颁发荣誉证书，执行校长范红铭为优秀指导老师颁发荣誉证书。随后，获奖学生代表许铭慧、优秀指导老师代表晏志鹏在会上发言。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-10%2016%3A28%3A07%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20231110162719.jpg?Expires=2014964888&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=CXuPYESXgj9jWVVtaln8vBhMV9c%3D" alt="" width="650" height="366" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-10%2016%3A28%3A28%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20231110162730.jpg?Expires=2014964908&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=C4CM4oeDSvnYcQiwNl74KZXfdbE%3D" alt="" width="650" height="366" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-10%2016%3A31%3A13IMG_8822.JPG?Expires=2014965073&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=eGJKuN7D3MYc3549EzuBBIHAcUg%3D" alt="" width="650" height="367" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 25pt; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-10%2016%3A31%3A34IMG_8816.JPG?Expires=2014965094&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=W8KH0rBfAaCPKDKWxoMgJPdz6eU%3D" alt="" width="650" height="328" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 26pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">执行校长范红铭在会上作题为《技能让生活更美好》的讲话，向职业技能大比武获奖的同学表示热烈的祝贺，对指导教师所付出的辛勤劳动表示衷心的感谢！</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 26pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 26pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-11-10%2016%3A32%3A26%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20231110162738.jpg?Expires=2014965146&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=TBDi6C1dumj00hdnOekTL4Cgy6s%3D" alt="" width="650" height="366" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 26pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">他指出，以赛促学、以赛促教是我校多年来保持的优良传统，是培养高素质技术技能人才的重要举措。这次职业技能大比武参照了江西省职业院校职业技能大赛和江西省大学生科技创新与技能大赛的要求，体现了专业的核心技术技能，展示了学生的综合职业技能。大赛设有区块链知识与技术应用竞赛、程序设计竞赛、大数据应用技术竞赛等23个技能比赛项目，比赛项目丰富，专业性强，参赛的学生近3500人次，共有305名学生获奖。希望同学们再接再厉，在各类竞赛中展示江软学子“学好软件，报效祖国”和“学技能、勇争先”的精神风貌。希望全体教师向获奖的优秀指导教师学习，人人争做理论功底深厚、技能技艺精湛的双师型教师，在不断提升专业技能和教学技能的同时，狠抓学生创新能力和实践技能的力量，为国家培养更多高素质技术技能人才、能工巧匠、大国工匠。</span></p><p><br/></p>